    "title": "Ultramyrmex abstractii",
    "description": "A poem I wrote:\n\nLife is an illness, acute and chronic. \nA visceral journey, ineffable, supersonic.\nInterpret patterns beyond Platonic.\nIdeals clashing, friction, tectonic. \n\nLeave Earth to find the realm of pure thought,\nFind the object that you honestly sought.\nThe hunter returns and shows what was caught, \nProof that the seeker's love is never for naught. \n\nThe straw alone is weak, become yourself a bundle. \nConstant revolt, this cookie never has to crumble. \nBecause even when the earthly body stumble,\nThe Universe will continue, infinite, humble. \n",
